Stephen Fulton and Brandon Figueroa will fight to unify junior featherweight titles on Nov. 27 at Park MGM in Las Vegas.

The fight was originally set for Sept. 18 but was postponed after Figueroa tested positive for COVID. (via @MikeCoppinger)

Tank Davis is back in the gym and he looks as fast as ever⚡️ 

(via @Gervontaa)
